          <TD width=150 bgColor=#e8e8e8 class=view align=middle vAlign=center><B>제 &nbsp; 목</B></FONT></TD>
          <TD width=450 bgColor=white class=view>&nbsp; &nbsp; <B>[종목돋보기]LG화학 "산넘어 산"</B></TD></TR>
        <TR>
          <TD bgColor=#e8e8e8 class=view align=middle vAlign=center><B>작성자</B></FONT></TD>
					<TD bgColor=white class=view>&nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=#010080><a href='mailto:sqkang@moneytoday.co.kr'>강상규</a> 이코노미스트 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 07/19 08:13 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 조회 3895 &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></TD></TR>
